{"tid":2409253,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"細個唔明點解上帝咁樣懲罰亞當","createTime":"2021-02-15T15:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T10:19:12.000Z","uid":35870,"like":184,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"19cc8ab596b8c8651ba5d015df383e962d6c41a4","tid":2409253,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"亞當食左禁果，上帝懲罰佢，要佢一世辛勞工作<br />\n以前唔明：呢d算咩懲罰？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"medium\"><em>主上帝對那男人說：「你既然聽從妻子的話，吃了我禁止你吃的果子，土地要因你違背命令而受詛咒。你要終生辛勞才能生產足夠的糧食。<br />\n<br />\n土地要長出荊棘雜草，而你要吃田間的野菜。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">你要汗流滿面才吃得飽。你要工作，直到你死</span>，歸於塵土；因為你是用塵土造的，你要還原歸土。」</em></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家開始明白，呢個係對人類最大嘅懲罰<br />\n<br />\n你要工作，直到你死<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"539c9e64e749069849c581045482bc41def347bb","tid":2409253,"uid":81214,"like":23,"dislike":15,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:45:11.000Z","msg":"收皮喇 耶撚<br />\n買美股發達最實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4794b18cf220173e65d22308d8dce4b07ba018f8","tid":2409253,"uid":56957,"like":109,"dislike":0,"score":109,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Bv42db.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Bv42db.gif&h=8325c6e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14ea012bb981071b101612ce798f80e2bda9cd3e","tid":2409253,"uid":389053,"like":25,"dislike":5,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ca8652747e6e67292e67bce401c48bcfa856a4c","tid":2409253,"uid":78243,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T16:32:42.000Z","msg":"第一個被上帝陷害既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b60bcbdc2ce467ff5c85ef85db604f341492c9","tid":2409253,"uid":268516,"like":52,"dislike":2,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T16:34:15.000Z","msg":"亞當最大嘅錯就係唔搞基<br />\n條女累死佢